132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 642
H.P. 410 House of Representatives, February 25, 2025
An Act to Provide Students in the University of Maine System Who
Are Parents or Pregnant Individuals Priority Registration for
Courses
Received by the Clerk of the House on February 20, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Education and Cultural Affairs pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant to
Joint Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative GRIFFIN of Levant.
Cosponsored by Representatives: COLLAMORE of Pittsfield, COLLINS of Sidney,
HAGGAN of Hampden, SMITH of Palermo.
Printed on recycled paper

1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 20-A MRSA §10912 is enacted to read:
3 §10912. Priority for parents or pregnant individuals to register for courses
4 The trustees shall ensure that a parent or pregnant individual who is enrolled at the
5 university receives priority in registering for courses for the purpose of scheduling the
6 courses around the parent's child care. The trustees shall distribute flyers and posters
7 informing students of the right of parents and pregnant individuals to priority registration
8 for courses. The posters must be displayed in appropriate places at each campus of the
9 university and on the publicly accessible website of each campus of the university.
10 SUMMARY
1111 This bill requires the Trustees of the University of Maine System to ensure that a parent
1122 or pregnant individual who is enrolled in the University of Maine System receives priority
1133 in registering for courses for the purpose of scheduling the courses around the parent's child
1144 care. This bill requires the trustees to distribute flyers and posters informing students of the
1155 right of parents and pregnant individuals to priority registration for courses. It also requires
1166 that the posters be displayed in appropriate places at each campus of the University of
1177 Maine System and on the publicly accessible website of each campus of the University of
1188 Maine System.
